a different educational level

00:36:08.170 --> 00:36:11.570
when one person a is writing
than when person B is writing.

00:36:11.570 --> 00:36:14.970
Either is fine for a sailor
in the Napoleonic era,

00:36:14.970 --> 00:36:16.310
but we should pick one.

00:36:16.310 --> 00:36:19.920
Like, these were bugs
in the spreadsheet when

00:36:19.920 --> 00:36:23.220
we were-- We were like, we
gotta fix that because so-and-so

