00:36:26.460 --> 00:36:33.680
And there were sometimes issues
between-- like, that's a design

00:36:33.680 --> 00:36:34.930
thing, as you were saying.

00:36:34.930 --> 00:36:37.570
That's a flavor thing, right?

00:36:37.570 --> 00:36:40.990
There were sometimes
issues with handoffs

00:36:40.990 --> 00:36:46.547
on the technical sense,
