00:36:46.547 --> 00:36:48.880
somebody wasn't setting a
flag that someone else needed,

00:36:48.880 --> 00:36:49.463
type of thing.

00:36:49.463 --> 00:36:50.880
And that was in the spreadsheet.

00:36:50.880 --> 00:36:53.932
I think that's just a
