00:37:11.049 --> 00:37:11.840
ANDREW GRANT: Sure.

00:37:11.840 --> 00:37:13.506
I like how you put
that, because you all

00:37:13.506 --> 00:37:16.917
have encountered the same
thing through code right now.

00:37:16.917 --> 00:37:17.750
LAURA BALDWIN: Yeah.

00:37:17.750 --> 00:37:21.530
I found that having, for any
given sort of tone thing,

00:37:21.530 --> 00:37:25.780
having one person who is
